In case you are running a `forEach`or `map` loop, and `prop.component` is just a reference to a component you can use [React.createElement](https://reactjs.org/docs/react-api.html#createelement) to build that element as **children** of the `Route` like:

```react
&lt;Route
path={prop.layout+prop.path}
key={key}
&gt;
 {React.createElement(prop.component,props)}
&lt;/Route&gt;
```

